high_descs: Turn left, go forward, turn right at the counter to the right of the sink.
Take the knife from the counter.
Stay at the counter.
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Step back from the counter.
Put the knife in a drawer under the microwave's left side.
Stay at the counter.
Take a slice of tomato from the counter.
Turn right, go forward, turn right at the microwave.
Cook the tomato slice in the microwave, take the tomato slice from the microwave.
Turn around, go forward to the wall, turn right to face the green bin, go to the bin.
Put the tomato slice in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of tomato in a bin.

high_descs: Turn to the left 90 degrees and walk a bit, turning to face the counter when you reach the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Look up at the cabinets above the counter.
Slice the tomato on the counter.
Turn around 360 degrees and open the drawer on your right, putting the knife inside.
Close the drawer with the knife inside.
Walk towards the counter in front of you.
Grab a slice of tomato from off of the counter.
Turn to the right 90 degrees and walk towards the microwave, turning to face it when you reach it.
Open the microwave, put the tomato inside, close it, cook the tomato, open the door when it finishes, remove the tomato, and close the door.
Turn around 180 degrees and cross the room.
Turn to the right 90 degrees and approach the trash can and place the tomato inside.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a cooked, sliced tomato in the trash can.

high_descs: Move to the back right of the counter to the right of the sink
Pick up the knife on the counter top
Slice the tomato on top of the counter in the back
Carry the knife over to the drawer underneath the red microwave
Spin around in a circle then face the drawer
Place the knife in the drawer
Move to face the tomato on the counter top
Pick up a slice of tomato
Carry the tomato to the microwave
Place the tomato in the microwave, turn it on, then remove, shut the door
Marry the tomato slice to the green bin at the edge of the counter top
Place the tomato in the green bin
anns.task_desc: Cut a microwaved slice of tomato to place in the trash
